{"tid":2153373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［撐蘋果］支持一日唔夠 要日日架","createTime":"2020-08-12T13:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T15:21:01.000Z","uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f88ec254ba601a09933c3791fadd6d138b3cc8c","tid":2153373,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:09:38.000Z","msg":"每朝買一份報紙咁平都唔keep住日日做<br />\n<br />\n買份報紙支持公司實業 公司預期有一定數量需求多印報紙其實對公司好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n股價都hold唔住今日開始插水 <br />\n<br />\n炒起市值係有幫助 到肥佬黎要減持兌返錢都多啲丫 <br />\n<br />\n今日先有報導話佢要賣物業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩者都堅持唔到就開始比五毛藍絲笑架啦<br />\n<br />\n撐蘋果撐到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76821f66e5a41c9bc81ea44344357c675c7d1b58","tid":2153373,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"日日買我點解唔課金?<br />\n<br />\n點解要比咁多中間人抽水"},{"pid":"34fbb0c750d8344261c56d53f654b330ea6fb18e","tid":2153373,"uid":273576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n聽日落小廣告"},{"pid":"41ae5a5ea7c22d732c99716dc11f37b780a1a9fb","tid":2153373,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76821f66e5a41c9bc81ea44344357c675c7d1b58","tid":2153373,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"日日買我點解唔課金?<br />\n<br />\n點解要比咁多中間人抽水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"課金都係一種做法<br />\n咁當然訂閱個d唔洗講<br />\n日日買報都係支持<br />\n托住個價亦都係 原因如上述<br />\n總之各個方式無衝突既 做到盡做"},{"pid":"58e0a3981a628f69fc1095e3ae445cc07d29a3d3","tid":2153373,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVnL00i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVnL00i.png&h=cad21905&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYOWodE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2